<footer class="footer-section">
    <div class="footer-main bg-white pt-5 pb-4 border-top border-success border-3">
        <div class="container text-md-start text-center">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4 col-xl-4 mx-auto mt-3">
                    <h5 class="mb-3 footer-brand">
                        <i class="fas fa-utensils me-2 text-success"></i>@CookingShare.Helpers.SettingHelper.GetValue("SiteName", "CookingShare")
                    </h5>
                    <p class="text-secondary pe-lg-5 mb-3">
                        Nền tảng chia sẻ công thức nấu ăn hàng đầu Việt Nam. Nơi kết nối những tâm hồn yêu bếp và lan tỏa hương vị yêu thương.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-3">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm rounded-circle me-2" title="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm rounded-circle me-2" title="YouTube"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm rounded-circle me-2" title="TikTok"><i class="fab fa-tiktok"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-sm rounded-circle" title="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mt-3">
                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-4 fw-bold text-success footer-heading">Khám phá</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Tip")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Mẹo vặt</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Thực đơn Healthy</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Đặc sản vùng miền</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Bếp bánh</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mt-3">
                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-4 fw-bold text-success footer-heading">Hỗ trợ</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Giới thiệu</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Hỗ trợ</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Chính sách bảo mật</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a href="@Url.Action("UnderConstruction", "Error")" class="footer-link text-decoration-none text-secondary">Quy tắc cộng đồng</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-3 mx-auto mt-3">
                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-4 fw-bold text-success footer-heading">Liên hệ</h6>
                    <p class="text-secondary mb-2"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt me-2 text-warning"></i> 123 Cù Lao Giêng, An Giang</p>

                    <p class="text-secondary mb-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2 text-warning"></i>
                        @CookingShare.Helpers.SettingHelper.GetValue("ContactEmail", "contact@cookingshare.com")
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-secondary mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt me-2 text-warning"></i>
                        @CookingShare.Helpers.SettingHelper.GetValue("Hotline", "0912.345.678")
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom bg-dark text-white py-3">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                    <p class="mb-0 small">
                        &copy; @DateTime.Now.Year <strong>@CookingShare.Helpers.SettingHelper.GetValue("SiteName", "CookingShare")</strong>. All Rights Reserved.
                        <span class="d-none d-sm-inline mx-2">|</span> <br class="d-sm-none">
                        Designed by <span class="text-success fw-bold">Hoang Anh</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .footer-link {
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #ff6600 !important;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }
</style>